title: Lille vs Nantes - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 16
description: Lille have not lost to Nantes in Ligue 1 since September 2015, a 1-0 success for the Canaries in the North. Les Dogues are on a 17-game unbeaten run against FCN, the longest run in their history in the top-flight against the same opponent. Lille have not lost any of their last 17 matches in all competitions, the second longest unbeaten streak in their history after a 19-game run between October 1973 and March 1974.

title: Olympique Lyonnais vs Montpellier - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 16
description: Lyon and Montpellier will face each other for the 60th time in Ligue 1. Among the current clubs in the top-flight, MHSC are the third team against which Les Gones have won most often, behind Strasbourg and Angers. Montpellier have lost five of their last six meetings with Lyon, having won each of the previous three. MHSCs last two wins over OL have come on the road.

title: Olympique Marseille vs Le Havre - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 16
description: Marseille are on a 20-game unbeaten run against Le Havre in Ligue 1, having only had a longer streak without defeat against a single opponent once before. OM even has a 100%-win rate in six matches against Le Havre in Ligue 1 in the 21st century, the opponent they have faced the most over that period while posting such a perfect record. Marseille have lost only one of their 20 home matches against Le Havre in Ligue 1 and it came in the first of those back in December 1938. OM have only faced Bastia more often at home while losing at most once in the top-flight.

title: Lens vs Toulouse - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 16
description: Lens have won each of their last six Ligue 1 matches against Toulouse and could establish their longest winning streak in the top-flight against a single opponent. title: Brest vs Olympique Lyonnais - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 17
description: Brest have won just six of their 25 matches against Lyon in Ligue 1, but all of their victories have come at home. The Bretons have the opportunity to win consecutive home games against Lyon in L1 for the first time since 1979-1982. Brest have nine fewer points after 16 Ligue 1 matches in 2024/25 than at the same stage last season, the biggest negative differential among the teams present in the top flight over the period. Conversely, Lyon have the best differential.

title: Reims vs Nice - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 17
description: Reims have lost 26 of their 72 Ligue 1 games against Nice, only losing more against St Etienne. SdR remain on an 11-match winless streak in the top-flight against OGCN and are only on a longer run against Lens. Fixtures between Reims and Nice produce an average of 1.4 goals per game in Ligue 1 in the 21st century, the lowest among fixtures played more than 10 times since 2001. Six of the last eight top-flight games between SdR and OGCN have ended 0-0, including each of the last two at Stade Auguste-Delaune.

title: Le Havre vs Lens - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 17
description: Le Havre have only lost 10% of their home games against Lens in the 21st century in all competitions, having a lower percentage against no other team they’ve faced at least 10 times at their stadium. title: Rennes vs Olympique Marseille - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 17

title: Nantes vs Monaco - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 17
